{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"681ae227a7","title":"关于土改和农业合作化","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3f6c8e19dc","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"681ae227a7"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"1b39e05593","name":"薛书云"},{"id":"5c242baf00","name":"陈光祖"},{"id":"879a0e7312","name":"吕庆仕"},{"id":"8d145154e0","name":"刘进仕"},{"id":"914865708e","name":"孙澜"},{"id":"953e8a8781","name":"贠虎章"},{"id":"e06664a15f","name":"李伯歧"},{"id":"ea25ac8f66","name":"西北农学院"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"30877920a6","type":"title","text":"关于土改和农业合作化","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"681ae227a7"},{"id":"a568d34e0d","type":"authors","text":"西北农学院刘进仕吕庆仕贠虎章陈光祖孙澜李伯武薛书云","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"681ae227a7"},{"id":"3c9800d795","type":"paragraph","text":"1．“土改中我家被分，我父亲是勤劳的，为什么给分了。”“土改使我的父亲受了委曲，被冤枉了，父亲根本没有什么罪恶。”“父亲放高利贷是救济人，很慈善。”(农60级学生　刘进仕)","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"681ae227a7"},{"id":"4f99db2123","type":"paragraph","text":"3．土改时分了他家的地，他说：“要是早知道，我早卖了可以改善生活。”(植60级学生  吕庆仕)","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"681ae227a7"},{"id":"7148dbf639","type":"paragraph","text":"4．“土改后剩下的果园已入社了，最后一点希望也完了。”(农60级学生　刘进仕)","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"681ae227a7"},{"id":"dcad574504","type":"paragraph","text":"5．“合作化搞的没有解放前地主的大队人马下地威风，地主一个管家把生产组织的比现在还好。”“解放前村里大骡子人马很多，解放后不见了，合作社喂牲口喂的不好，大量死牛，农民不愿意把骡子马交给社里，从地主那里分下就卖了。”(水58级学生　贠虎章)","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"681ae227a7"},{"id":"2470fea49e","type":"paragraph","text":"6．“农业合作化农村尽是死牛，还没有过去地主管家管的好。”(水58级学生　陈光祖)","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"681ae227a7"},{"id":"b2f9dfe07a","type":"paragraph","text":"8．“合作社真要把人整困死。”(经60级学生　孙澜)","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"681ae227a7"},{"id":"dc56ccc16d","type":"paragraph","text":"9．“现在农业社都是强迫加入，强迫加入的有90％。”(水59级学生　李伯武)","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"681ae227a7"},{"id":"62b5c5b930","type":"paragraph","text":"10．“合作社不见得比单干能增产，未合作化单干还够吃。”(林59级学生　薛书云)","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"681ae227a7"},{"id":"d4a121d111","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《西北农学院右派言论及错误言论汇集》(西北农学院马列主义教研组编印，1957年12月)。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"681ae227a7"}],"page":{"id":"3a02afbd67","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"681ae227a7","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}